**/plain_modules/
**/conformance_tests/
**/build/
**/build_conformance_tests/
**/dist/
**/dist_conformance_tests/
**/codeplain.log
**/*.log

# Generator residue: byte-compiled Python and nested git checkouts the
# Codeplain build leaves inside generated module/conformance trees.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/.git/
.pytest_cache/
**/node_modules/
# `npm i` run by the conformance test command in a dir with no package.json
# leaves an empty lockfile; keep it out of the tree.
**/package-lock.json
